    <div class="callout info">
      <div class="callout-title">📌 Learning objectives</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Choose appropriate architecture patterns and understand trade-offs</li>
        <li>Design APIs for reliability, streaming UX, and operational safety</li>
        <li>Apply scaling patterns (load balancing, autoscaling) to AI workloads</li>
        <li>Plan for observability, security, and failure modes in production</li>
